{"surahDetails":{"id":86,"arabicName":"الطارق","banglaName":"রাতের আগন্তুক","englishName":"The Morning Star","enTranslatedName":"At-Tariq","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":61,"totalLetters":249,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/86.mp3","totalAyah":17},"surah":{"id":86,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","bangl_text":"শপথ আকাশের এবং রাত্রিতে আগমনকারীর।","english_text":"By the sky and the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5932.mp3","colorText":"وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓءِ وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>طَّارِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ق</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","bangl_text":"আপনি জানেন, যে রাত্রিতে আসে সেটা কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what is the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5933.mp3","colorText":"وَم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</tajweed>كَ مَا <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>طَّارِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ق</tajweed>ُ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱلنَّجۡمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","bangl_text":"সেটা এক উজ্জ্বল নক্ষত্র।","english_text":"It is the piercing star","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5934.mp3","colorText":"ٱ<tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=qalaqah>جْ</tajweed>مُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>ثَّاقِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed>ُ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"إِن كُلّ