>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>تَّر<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓئِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجۡعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় তিনি তাকে ফিরিয়ে নিতে সক্ষম।","english_text":"Indeed, Allah, to return him [to life], is Able","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5939.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> عَلَىٰ رَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>جْ</tajweed>عِه<tajweed class=madda_normal>ِۦ</tajweed> لَقَادِرٌ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"يَوۡمَ تُبۡلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","bangl_text":"যেদিন গোপন বিষয়াদি পরীক্ষিত হবে","english_text":"The Day when secrets will be put on trial","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5940.mp3","colorText":"يَوْمَ تُ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>لَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّر<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓئِرُ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٖ وَلَا نَاصِرٖ","bangl_text":"সেদিন তার কোন শক্তি থাকবে না এবং সাহায্যকারীও থাকবে না।","english_text":"Then man will have no power or any helper","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5941.mp3","colorText":"فَمَا لَهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> مِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ق</tajweed>ُوَّ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ةٍ و</tajweed>َلَا نَاصِرٍ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجۡعِ","bangl_text":"শপথ চক্রশীল আকাশের","english_text":"By the sky which returns [rain]","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5942.mp3","colorText":"وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓءِ ذَاتِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>رَّ<tajweed class=qalaqah>جْ</tajweed>عِ <span class=end>١١</span>"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدۡعِ","bangl_text":"এবং বিদারনশীল পৃথিবীর","english_text":"And [by] the earth which cracks open","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5943.mp3","colorText":"وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>صَّ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>عِ <span class=end>١٢</span>"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلٞ فَصۡلٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কোরআন সত্য-মিথ্যার ফয়সালা।","english_text":"Indeed, the Qur'an is a decisive statement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5944.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> لَقَوْ<tajweed class=ikhafa>لٌ ف</tajweed>َصْلٌ <span class=end>١٣</span>"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ","bangl_text":"এবং এটা উপহাস নয়।","english_text":"And it is not amusement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5945.mp3","colorText":"وَمَا هُوَ بِ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْهَزْلِ <span class=end>١٤</span>"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَكِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"তারা ভীষণ চক্রান্ত করে","english_text":"Indeed, they are planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5946.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهُمْ يَكِيدُونَ كَيْدًا <span class=end>١٥</span>"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"আর আমিও কৌশল করি।","english_text":"But I am planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5947.mp3","colorT